								type[]=
								{
									"STRING"
								};
							};
							value="Use the ""Request Reinsert"" option at the base flag to insert the squad into the field (or AAC).  Once in the field try to secure the areas around the other landing sites to allow for better flow of logistics. Leaders can move the landing sites using their support action in self-interact, you are free to select any of the landing sites for your initial insert.<br/><br/>All reinserts will be delivered in the same manner if you choose to play this way, be advised that an MHQ is available in the field at HLS Teacup if you wish to play that way.<br/><br/>Support can be gained by inserting friendly forces to assist in your assaults or by using the Drone with 6 x Brimstone Missiles, UAV Terminal found in Gearbox.";
