			description="Small resupply crates meant only for a fire-teams resupply. The Ammo Boxes have the standard ammunition for the Squad, the Special Weapons Crate has the secondary ammunitions such as for the roles of MAT, AMAT, AMMG, MMG, Light Rifleman, Marksman.";
